<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media -- Advertising:
   Grey Wins Domino's From Ross Roy Unit
   ----
   By John B. Hinge
</HL>
<DATE>
04/17/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   EK GREY IPG PCI
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
CONSUMER NON-CYCLICAL (NCY)
</MS>
